data.value: SELECT M.EmpCode,P.SecDescription AS PositionKH,D.SecDescription AS DeptKH,S.SecDescription AS SectKH,M.OthAllName,M.Sex, P.SortKey AS SortPost,B.SecDescription AS BranchKH,OT.OTStartTime,OT.OTEndTime,OT.Hours, CASE WHEN OT.Reason IS NOT NULL THEN OT.Reason ELSE OT.Remark END Reson FROM HRRequestOT OT LEFT JOIN HRStaffProfile M ON M.EmpCode=OT.EmpCode LEFT JOIN HRBranch B ON B.Code=M.Branch LEFT JOIN HRDepartment D ON D.Code=M.DEPT LEFT JOIN HRSection S ON S.Code=M.SECT LEFT JOIN HRPosition P ON P.Code=M.JobCode WHERE OT.EmpCode IN (SELECT * FROM dbo.SplitString(@EmpCode, ';')) AND OT.Status='PENDING' AND DAY(OT.OTEndTime)=DAY(@InMonth) AND MONTH(OT.OTEndTime)=MONTH(@InMonth) AND YEAR(OT.OTEndTime)=YEAR(@InMonth)
